    {
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "当时，因为战争结束的关系，我们这一级面临着被取消的风险。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgmDelay": 2,
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "后来几经坎坷，我们才终于得以降生。",
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "不过因为战争已经结束，我们即使降生了，也没有体验过前辈们那种波澜壮阔的生活。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "如果说不向往，那我一定是在否定自己的价值。",
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "半人马淡淡地诉说着。",
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "不过，不只是这样的。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "指挥官，我的生涯是在和平之中度过的，我没有体会过战争的伤痛。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "但我在了解前辈们事迹的同时，也明白了战争是什么样的东西。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "那绝不是未曾体验过其残酷的我，能够轻率地挂在嘴边的东西。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "所以，我才更加憧憬和尊敬那些参与过那场战争，并且将其终结的前辈们",
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 2,
      "say": "说实在的，光是“前辈”两个字，完全无法表达我对各位的敬意呢。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "半人马看来也是自己深思熟虑过的。",
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "不过，确实，要是我的坚持给各位添麻烦了那就本末倒置了。",
